---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="ICRA 2026 Africa Satellite — AARC"
  description="The Akili African Robotics Community is hosting an official IEEE ICRA 2026 Satellite Conference Center — bringing the world's leading robotics conference to Africa via live-streamed keynotes, panels, and tutorials."
>

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pt-12 pb-24 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="reveal mb-16">
      <a href="/" class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-orange-300 transition-colors">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
        Back to home
      </a>
      <p class="mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-orange-300/90">Upcoming Event · 2&ndash;4 June 2026</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">IEEE <span class="nasal-title">ICRA</span> 2026</h1>
      <p class="mb-8 text-2xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-300 leading-snug">Africa Satellite Conference Center</p>
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-400">
        AARC is proud to host an official Satellite Conference Center for the IEEE International Conference
        on Robotics and Automation 2026 &mdash; bringing the world&rsquo;s flagship robotics conference to
        Africa, live from Vienna.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-orange-400/25 bg-orange-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-200 uppercase tracking-widest">Live Streaming</span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-cyan-400/25 bg-cyan-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-cyan-200 uppercase tracking-widest">In-Person</span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-emerald-400/25 bg-emerald-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-200 uppercase tracking-widest">Free to Attend</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- About -->
    <div class="reveal panel rounded-3xl p-8 mb-10">
      <p class="mb-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-orange-300/80">About</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-white">Bringing ICRA to Africa</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-300">
        The <strong class="text-white">IEEE International Conference on Robotics and Automation (ICRA)</strong>
        is the world&rsquo;s largest and most influential gathering of robotics researchers and practitioners.
        ICRA 2026 takes place <strong class="text-white">1&ndash;5 June 2026 in Vienna, Austria</strong>, and for
        many African researchers, attending in person is prohibitive due to cost, visa logistics, and travel time.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-300">
        ICRA&rsquo;s <strong class="text-white">Satellite Conference Center</strong> programme exists to close
        that gap. AARC is hosting Africa&rsquo;s satellite center at <strong class="text-white">Wits University,
        Johannesburg</strong> &mdash; offering live-streamed access to opening sessions, keynotes, panels, and
        tutorials, alongside a local programme of networking, lightning talks, and lab visits curated for the
        African robotics community.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-300">
        This builds on AARC&rsquo;s previous successful collaboration with IEEE &mdash; the
        <strong class="text-white">ICRA@40 Africa Satellite Event</strong> hosted at Wits in 2024.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-orange-400/15 bg-orange-400/5 p-5">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-orange-200">At a Glance</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span><strong class="text-white">When:</strong>&nbsp;2&ndash;4 June 2026 (live-stream days)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span><strong class="text-white">Where:</strong>&nbsp;University of the Witwatersrand, Johannesburg, South Africa</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span><strong class="text-white">Format:</strong>&nbsp;Live-streamed ICRA sessions + local programme</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span><strong class="text-white">Cost:</strong>&nbsp;Free to attend (registration required)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span><strong class="text-white">Open to:</strong>&nbsp;Researchers, students, engineers, and industry practitioners</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- What you'll experience -->
    <div class="reveal mb-4">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-orange-300/90">Programme</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">What you&rsquo;ll experience</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-400">
        Attendees will have direct access to ICRA&rsquo;s flagship sessions, broadcast live from Vienna,
        complemented by an on-the-ground programme designed to spark conversation and collaboration here in Africa.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal panel rounded-3xl p-8 mb-10">
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Opening Session</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">The official ICRA 2026 kick-off, live from Vienna</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Keynote & Industry Keynote Sessions</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Leading voices from academia and industry</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Plenary Sessions</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Big-picture talks shaping the future of robotics</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Panel Discussions</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Expert conversations on the field&rsquo;s biggest questions</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-cyan-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Keynote Tutorials</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Deep-dive technical sessions from leading researchers</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-cyan-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Award Lunch Session</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Celebrating the year&rsquo;s outstanding contributions to robotics</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Local Lightning Talks</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">A platform for African researchers to share their work</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Networking & Lab Visits</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Connect with the African robotics community in person</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Attend -->
    <div class="reveal mb-4">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-orange-300/90">Why Attend</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Three reasons to be there</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal panel rounded-3xl p-8 mb-6">
      <div class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-orange-400/20 bg-orange-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-200 uppercase tracking-widest">Reason 1</div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Access without the airfare</h3>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-300">
        ICRA is the most important conference in robotics, and historically the cost of attending in person has
        kept it out of reach for most African researchers and students. Our satellite center brings the same
        sessions &mdash; live, in real time &mdash; to Johannesburg, for free.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal panel rounded-3xl p-8 mb-6">
      <div class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-orange-400/20 bg-orange-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-200 uppercase tracking-widest">Reason 2</div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Connect with the African robotics community</h3>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-300">
        Streaming ICRA from your laptop is one thing. Watching it alongside other African roboticists &mdash;
        and joining the conversations that happen between sessions &mdash; is entirely another. Expect to leave
        with new collaborators, mentors, and friends across the continent.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal panel rounded-3xl p-8 mb-10">
      <div class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-orange-400/20 bg-orange-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-200 uppercase tracking-widest">Reason 3</div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Be part of putting African robotics on the global map</h3>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-300">
        Hosting an official ICRA satellite center signals that Africa is part of the global robotics
        conversation &mdash; not as observers, but as contributors. Your participation helps build the case for
        a future where ICRA itself comes to the continent.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Schedule -->
    <div class="reveal mb-4">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-orange-300/90">Schedule</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Three-day programme</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-400">
        Sessions broadcast live from Vienna and shown in local time (SAST, UTC+2). Local programming runs
        between live streams. This schedule is tentative and will be finalised closer to the event.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal mb-10 overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
            <th class="py-3 px-4 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-orange-300/80 text-left w-[180px]">Day</th>
            <th class="py-3 px-4 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-orange-300/80 text-left">Morning</th>
            <th class="py-3 px-4 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-orange-300/80 text-left">Afternoon</th>
            <th class="py-3 px-4 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-orange-300/80 text-left">Evening</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-white/5 text-slate-300">
          <tr>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 align-top">
              <div class="text-white font-semibold">Day 1</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Tue, 2 June 2026</div>
            </td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 align-top">
              <div class="text-orange-200/90">Welcome &amp; Registration</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Local opening</div>
            </td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 align-top">
              <div class="text-orange-200/90">ICRA Opening Session</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Live from Vienna</div>
            </td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 align-top">
              <div class="text-emerald-300/80">Networking Reception</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Local programme</div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 align-top">
              <div class="text-white font-semibold">Day 2</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Wed, 3 June 2026</div>
            </td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 align-top">
              <div class="text-orange-200/90">Keynote &amp; Plenary</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Live from Vienna</div>
            </td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 align-top">
              <div class="text-cyan-300/80">Keynote Tutorial</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Live from Vienna</div>
            </td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 align-top">
              <div class="text-emerald-300/80">Local Lightning Talks</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">African researchers in the spotlight</div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 align-top">
              <div class="text-white font-semibold">Day 3</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Thu, 4 June 2026</div>
            </td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 align-top">
              <div class="text-orange-200/90">Industry Keynote</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Live from Vienna</div>
            </td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 align-top">
              <div class="text-violet-300/80">Panel Discussion</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Live from Vienna</div>
            </td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 align-top">
              <div class="text-amber-300/80">RAIL Lab Visit &amp; Closing</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Wits University tour</div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <!-- Venue -->
    <div class="reveal mb-4">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-orange-300/90">Venue</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Hosted at Wits University</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal panel rounded-3xl p-8 mb-10">
      <p class="leading-8 text-slate-300">
        The satellite event will be held at the <strong class="text-white">University of the Witwatersrand</strong>
        in Johannesburg &mdash; home to the RAIL Lab, the MIND Institute, and one of the largest robotics and
        machine learning communities on the continent. Wits previously hosted AARC&rsquo;s ICRA@40 Africa
        satellite event in 2024.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-300">
        Specific room and arrival details will be shared with registered attendees closer to the date.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Closing CTA -->
    <div class="reveal panel orange-glow rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-orange-300/90">Register your interest</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">Be part of ICRA 2026 &mdash; in Africa.</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-slate-300 leading-7">
        Spaces at the satellite center are limited. Join our Discord to get the registration link as soon as
        it opens, and to stay across speaker announcements and programme updates.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://discord.gg/pvXMR8vcpV" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="primary-btn">Join our Discord</a>
        <a href="https://2026.ieee-icra.org/satellite-conference-centers/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="secondary-btn">About ICRA Satellites</a>
        <a href="/" class="secondary-btn">Back to home</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-white/10 px-6 py-10 text-sm text-slate-500">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Akili African Robotics Community</p>
      <p>Robotics &middot; AI &middot; Research &middot; Africa</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
